    "import mushi\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from scipy.special import expit\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import matplotlib.colors as colors"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 44,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "m = 10\n",
    "t = np.logspace(0, 5, m)\n",
    "change_points = t[:-1]\n",
    "y = 1e3 * (1 + 2 * expit(100 * (t - 1e3)) + 10 * expit(-100 * (t - 1e2)))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 45,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "eta = mushi.eta(t[:-1], y)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 46,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {

    }

   "source": [
    "eta.plot();"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 49,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "n = 10\n",
    "ksfs = mushi.kSFS(n=n)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 50,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [

     "data": {

    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.plot(change_points, ksfs.tmrca_cdf(eta))\n",
    "plt.xlabel('$t$ (generations ago)')\n",
    "plt.xscale('log')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('TMRCA CDF')\n",
    "plt.ylim([0, 1]);"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "source": [
    "mu0 = 100\n",
    "ksfs.simulate(eta, mu0, seed=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "ksfs.plot_total();\n",
    "plt.xscale('log')\n",
    "plt.yscale('log')"
   ]

   "source": [
    "alpha_tv_trajectory = np.logspace(2, 5, 10)\n",
    "alpha_spline_trajectory = np.logspace(1, 6, 10)\n",
    "residuals = np.zeros((len(alpha_tv_trajectory), len(alpha_spline_trajectory), m))\n",
    "loss = np.zeros((len(alpha_tv_trajectory), len(alpha_spline_trajectory)))\n",
    "etas = {}\n",
    "for i, alpha_tv in enumerate(alpha_tv_trajectory):\n",
    "    print(f'alpha_tv = {alpha_tv}')\n",
    "    for j, alpha_spline in enumerate(alpha_spline_trajectory):\n",
    "        print(f'    alpha_spline = {alpha_spline}')\n",
    "        ksfs.clear_eta()\n",
    "        ksfs.infer_history(change_points, mu0, max_iter=100,\n",
    "                           alpha_tv=alpha_tv, alpha_spline=alpha_spline, alpha_ridge=1e-6)\n",
    "\n",
    "        residuals[i, j, :] = np.log(ksfs.eta.y) - np.log(eta.y)\n",
    "        L = mushi.utils.C(n) @ mushi.utils.M(n, *ksfs.eta.arrays())\n",
    "        loss[i, j] = mushi.utils.prf(ksfs.mu.Z, ksfs.X, L)        \n",
    "        etas[i, j] = ksfs.eta"
   ]
  },
